# Common Mistakes

### ❌ Using `for` Loop Inside JSX

```jsx
{
    for(let i = 0; i < fruits.length; i++) {}
}
```

Not allowed.

Use

```jsx
fruits.map(...)
```

---

### ❌ Forgetting `key`

```jsx
students.map(student => (

    <div>

        {student.name}

    </div>

))
```

React Warning:

```
Each child in a list should have a unique "key" prop.
```

Correct

```jsx
<div key={student.id}>
```

